    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"39\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=39&amp;height=39\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"40\" data-width=\"40\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638868\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmShelfLightFilter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638842\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"08350f2c-515a-4c94-942c-8f6037396b6b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=40&amp;height=40 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=39&amp;height=39 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilterMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=140\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilterMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"140\" data-width=\"200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638871\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmShelfLightFilterMenu.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638842\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c8a087b1-1cde-4446-b0e0-2c094ddce66e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilterMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=140 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/rfmShelfLightFilterMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=140 1x\"></span><p> </p><p>Light Filters are used to manipulate lighting results. In the real world this is often achieved through the use of stencils and gels to change the color, quality, and amount of light in a shot. RenderMan's light filters are a powerful and flexible way to do the same (and even more) in lighting your scenes. </p><h3 id=\"LightFiltersinBlender-CreateLightFilters\">Create Light Filters</h3><p>To add a light filter to a light, first create a light filter from the Add menu:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/add_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=530&amp;height=240\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638842/add_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"240\" data-width=\"530\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638874\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"add_light_filter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638842\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3f52faef-f959-4f6a-9de7-49f2507197e8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/add_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=530&amp;height=240 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/add_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432709811&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=530&amp;height=240 1x\"></span><p>Next, select the light you want to be filter, and look at the object properties panel. You should see a Light Filters panel. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/light_filters_panel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=121\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638842/light_filters_panel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"121\" data-width=\"412\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638877\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_filters_panel.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638842\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fe57aef3-d4ef-4b52-ae27-0575ff5f4de8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/light_filters_panel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=121 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/light_filters_panel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=121 1x\"></span><p>Click the <strong>+ </strong>to add a new entry, then select which light filter object you want to link to.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/light_filters_panel2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=136\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638842/light_filters_panel2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"136\" data-width=\"414\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638880\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_filters_panel2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638842\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"854a41d5-c4c2-415d-8962-51a565917048\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/light_filters_panel2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=136 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/light_filters_panel2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=136 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"LightFiltersinBlender-Shortcut\">Shortcut</h3><p>You can also use the shortcut in the object context menu. Select the light you want to filter and select the light filter you want to add from the Attach New Light Filter menu. The new light filter will automatically be added to the light filters list.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/attach_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=591&amp;height=272\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638842/attach_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"272\" data-width=\"591\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638883\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"attach_light_filter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638842\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ba9243f4-68ac-4b10-bc90-d56b1515dfcf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/attach_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=591&amp;height=272 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638842/attach_light_filter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432710102&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=591&amp;height=272 1x\"></span><p /><h3 id=\"LightFiltersinBlender-LightFilterTypes\">Light Filter Types</h3><p>For detailed information about parameters, follow the links for each light filter type.</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661733\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrBarnLightFilter</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661753\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrBlockerLightFilter</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661755\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrCookieLightFilter</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661757\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrGoboLightFilter</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661767\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrIntMultLightFilter</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661759\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrRampLightFilter</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661773\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrRodLightFilter</a></p></li></ul>"
    }
  },
